The paper deals with wireless channel prediction, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of Gaussian processes for prediction falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and the paper also discusses the impact of location uncertainty, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
